<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="outlook-n">outlook <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'aʊtlʊk/    美 /'aʊtlʊk/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>观点；见解</strong></h4>
<p>your general attitude to life and the world：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He is a man with an optimistic <strong>outlook on</strong> life.
他是个对生活乐观的人。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>[常用单数] 展望；前景</strong></h4>
<p>what will probably happen：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The <strong>outlook for</strong> world peace is bright.
世界和平的前景是光明的。</p></div></div>